#: Game.Levels.GroupTutorial.L03_RightInverse
msgid "Every element in a group has an inverse. §0 tells you\n"
"that §1 — the element and its inverse cancel on the right.\n"
"\n"
"Notice that §2 found the pattern §3 inside\n"
"the larger expression §4. The §5 tactic searches for\n"
"the pattern anywhere in the goal, not just at the top level.\n"
"\n"
"But what about the other order? What is §6?"
msgstr ""

