#. §12: `Subgroup.mem_center_iff`
#. §13: `z ∈ center G ↔ ∀ g, g * z = z * g`
#. §14: `Subgroup.eq_top_iff'`
#. §15: `H = ⊤ ↔ ∀ x, x ∈ H`
#. §16: `[CommGroup G]`
#. §17: `mul_comm`
#. §18: `[Group G]`
#. §19: `CommGroup`
#. §20: `Group`
