#: Game.Levels.SubgroupDef.L07_BuildingTrivial
msgid "You just built a subgroup from scratch! The **trivial subgroup**\n"
"§0 is the smallest possible subgroup of any group.\n"
"\n"
"The construction pattern you used will appear in every subgroup\n"
"construction:\n"
"\n"
"1. §1 — creates three obligations\n"
"2. For each obligation: §2 the hypotheses, §3 to unfold\n"
"   membership, then prove the mathematical claim.\n"
"\n"
"The trivial subgroup was easy because the carrier predicate (§4)\n"
"is very restrictive — there's only one element to worry about.\n"
"\n"
"In the next levels, you'll build subgroups with more interesting\n"
"carriers, where the closure proofs require real group algebra."
msgstr ""

