#: Game.Levels.GroupBasicsPset
msgid "Welcome to the **Group Basics Problem Set** — your first practice world.\n"
"\n"
"No new theorems or tactics to learn here, just fresh problems using\n"
"the tools you've already built. The goal is fluency: recognizing which\n"
"tool to reach for when a problem looks different from anything you've\n"
"practiced before.\n"
"\n"
"Your full toolkit is available — including the §0 tactic, which\n"
"is back after its absence in Group Basics. Level 1 demonstrates its\n"
"power. For the remaining levels, §1 is disabled to keep you sharp\n"
"on manual techniques.\n"
"\n"
"The boss: extend the shoes-and-socks lemma from two factors to three."
