"§3. This lets us write §4 instead of §5, and more\n"
"generally §6 instead of §7.\n"
"\n"
"The three basic lemmas are:\n"
"\n"
"- §8: §9\n"
"- §10: §11\n"
"- §12: §13\n"
"\n"
"These extend the §14 and §15 you already know from ℕ-powers.\n"
"\n"
"Use these to prove §16."
