#: Game.Levels.GroupBasics.L09_Boss
msgid "Congratulations on completing **Group Basics**!\n"
"\n"
"You proved the **shoes-and-socks lemma**: §0.\n"
"Compare this to the Tutorial boss: there, you showed\n"
"§1 by direct calculation. Here, you used\n"
"**inverse uniqueness** to skip the direct manipulation and let the\n"
"cancellation lemmas do the heavy lifting.\n"
"\n"
