msgstr ""

#. §0: `rw [mul_comm (a * b) c]`
#. §1: `c * (a * b) = c * b * a`
#. §2: `rw [mul_comm a b]`
#. §3: `a`
#. §4: `b`
#. §5: `c * (b * a) = c * b * a`
#. §6: `rw [← mul_assoc]`
#: Game.Levels.CommGroupIntro.L02_CommRearrange
