#. §10: `bab⁻¹ ∈ ker(f)`
#: Game.Levels.HomPset.L03_KernelConjugation
msgid "The kernel is closed under conjugation: if §0, then\n"
"§1 for every §2.\n"
"\n"
"A subgroup with this property is called **normal**. You'll prove\n"
"formally that every kernel is normal later in the course. For now,\n"
"notice the proof pattern:\n"
"\n"
"1. Unfold §3 at hypothesis and goal\n"
"2. Push §4 through the expression (§5, §6)\n"
"3. Substitute the kernel equation (§7)\n"
"4. Simplify the group algebra\n"
"\n"
"On paper: *Since §8, we have\n"
"§9,\n"
"so §10.*"
msgstr ""

