"of §4, you only need to check **one** equation (§5). You\n"
"don't need to separately check §6 — right inverses are\n"
"automatically two-sided. This is a special property of groups.\n"
"\n"
"This technique will power the rest of this world. Both the double-\n"
"inverse identity and the boss level use exactly this pattern:\n"
"§7, then close the multiplication\n"
"goal with cancellation lemmas."
msgstr ""

#: Game.Levels.GroupTutorial.L01_RightIdentity
msgid "Right Identity"
msgstr ""

#. §0: `pow_orderOf_eq_one`
