"To prove this, you need **induction on §3** — a technique you\n"
"already know from the Natural Number Game. The §4 tactic\n"
"splits the proof into two goals:\n"
"\n"
"1. **Base case** (§5): prove §6\n"
"2. **Induction step** (§7): assuming §8,\n"
"   prove §9\n"
"\n"
"Write §10 to begin. Lean will create two goals\n"
"named §11 and §12."
msgstr ""

