#: Game.Levels.CyclicGroups.L09_Boss
msgid "**Case** §0: this means §1\n"
"by §2. But §3 — contradiction.\n"
"\n"
"Use §4 to convert."
msgstr ""

#. §0: `y ∈ f.range ↔ y ∈ ⊤`
#. §1: `refine ⟨?_, ?_⟩`
#: Game.Levels.HomPset.L07_Boss
