#. §0: `rw [Subgroup.mem_zpowers_iff]`
#. §1: `∃ k : ℤ, g ^ k = g⁻¹`
#: Game.Levels.CyclicGroups.L02_ZpowersMem
msgid "Use §0 to convert the goal to\n"
"§1."
msgstr ""

#. §0: `(a * b) * (a * b) = a * a * (b * b)`
#. §1: `mul_mul_mul_comm`
#. §2: `exact mul_mul_mul_comm a b a b`
#: Game.Levels.HomDef.L07_BuildAHom
msgid "The goal is §0.\n"
"This is the interchange law §1.\n"
"\n"
"Try §2."
