#. §5: `⟨⟩`
#. §6: `\\<`
#. §7: `\\>`
#. §8: `And`
#. §9: `a`
#. §10: `H ⊓ K`
#: Game.Levels.SubgroupBasics.L06_AngleBrackets
msgid "In the last level, you extracted one half of a conjunction using §0.\n"
"Now you'll go the other direction: given two membership proofs,\n"
"*build* a conjunction to show something belongs to an intersection.\n"
"\n"
"If you have §1 and §2, you can build a proof\n"
"of §3 with **angle brackets**:\n"
"\n"
"§4\n"
"\n"
"The angle brackets §5 are typed §6 and §7. They build a\n"
"value of a structure type (here §8) from its components.\n"
"\n"
"Prove that §9 belongs to §10."
