#. §11: `a * b`
#. §12: `a * c`
#. §13: `rw [← h]`
#: Game.Levels.GroupBasics.L05_LeftCancel
msgid "If §0, can you conclude §1? In a group, yes —\n"
"this is the **left cancellation law**.\n"
"\n"
"The proof formalizes a move you already know from algebra:\n"
"**multiply both sides by the same thing**. To cancel §2 on the left,\n"
