"\n"
"You've used §6 to rewrite with a named theorem. You can\n"
"also use §7 where §8 is a hypothesis in your context. If\n"
"§9, then §10 replaces §11 with §12\n"
"(or use §13 for the reverse direction)."
msgstr ""

#. §0: `f a = f b → a = b`
#. §1: `ker(f) = ⊥`
#. §2: `∀ y, ∃ x, f x = y`
#. §3: `range(f) = ⊤`
#. §4: `ker = ⊥`
#. §5: `mem_bot`
#. §6: `x ∈ ⊥`
#. §7: `x = 1`
#. §8: `range = ⊤`
#. §9: `mem_top`
#. §10: `y ∈ ⊤`
#. §11: `True`
#. §12: `f`
