#: Game.Levels.HomPset.L02_RangeMulMem
msgid "The **image-reasoning move** from Kernel and Image, now with two witnesses:\n"
"\n"
"1. **Obtain** witnesses from the hypotheses\n"
"2. **Combine** them using the group operation\n"
