#. §1: `rw [hx]`
#. §2: `1 ∈ H`
#. §3: `exact one_mem H`
#: Game.Levels.SubgroupBasics.L04_BotLE
msgid "Now §0. Rewrite the goal with §1 to\n"
"change it to §2, then close with §3."
msgstr ""

#. §0: `Subgroup.mem_center_iff`
#. §1: `z ∈ Subgroup.center G ↔ ∀ g, g * z = z * g`
