msgid "§0 says:\n"
"\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"Use §2 to unfold center membership\n"
"in the goal, or §3 to unfold\n"
"it in a hypothesis.\n"
"\n"
"Example: if the goal is §4, then\n"
"§5 changes it to §6."
