#. §16: `mul_assoc`
#: Game.Levels.CommGroupIntro.L02_CommRearrange
msgid "When you write §0, Lean swaps the first §1 it\n"
"finds. With three or more factors, you need to **target** which\n"
"pair to swap by providing arguments: §2 swaps\n"
"§3 and §4 specifically, leaving other factors alone.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: rearrange §5 to §6.\n"
"\n"
"Remember that §7 means §8 (left association).\n"
"You'll need to combine §9 with §10 to move\n"
"factors around.\n"
"\n"
"**Strategy**: Think of this in two stages:\n"
"1. Swap §11 with §12 to get §13\n"
"2. Swap §14 with §15 inside the parentheses\n"
"3. Remove the parentheses with §16"
msgstr ""

